<div class="email-container">
  <h2>Verify your new email address</h2>
  <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
  <p>
    You requested to change your email address for your SubMinder account. To
    confirm this change, please click the button below.
  </p>

  <a href="<%= url %>" class="btn">Verify New Email</a>

  <p>This link is valid for <strong>1 hour</strong>.</p>
  <p>
    If you didn't request this change, please ignore this email. Your current
    email address will remain unchanged.
  </p>
</div>
